span></p>\n </blockquote> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile25.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2166DC4E5475635F0298C4\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">달콤하고 부드러운 '고구마 샌드위치'입니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile27.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2560964F5475CB010529F8\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">가염버터로 바삭하게 구워서 먹기 전부터 고소한 버터향이 군침돌게 하는데요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">겉은 바삭~ 짭조름하면서 속은 달콤 부드럽습니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">여기에 버터~ 견과류가 있어서 고소한 맛도 좋고요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile8.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F275D324F5475CB020B411D\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">좀 더 예쁘게 찍기위해서는 충분히 식혀서 썰어야 모양이 깔끔한데</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">사진보다 우선은 먹기위해 만든 것이니~</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">맛있게 먹으려고 뜨거울때 그냥 잘랐더니 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">테두리가 너덜너덜 지저분하네요. 이해하시죠?</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile22.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2540444F5475CB032A3AE0\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">고구마를 푸짐하게 넣은 것이라 든든해서 간식 뿐만 아니라 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">아침식사로도 좋은데요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">달콤한 맛이 아이들은 우유와~</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> 어른들은 아메리카노와 먹으면&nbsp;더욱 맛있답니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">요즘 저렴하고 맛있는 고구마로 샌드위치&nbsp;간식!! 추천합니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <div class=\"txc-textbox\" style=\"BORDER-TOP: #e7fdb5 1px solid; BORDER-RIGHT: #e7fdb5 1px solid; BORDER-BOTTOM: #e7fdb5 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; BORDER-LEFT: #e7fdb5 1px solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #e7fdb5\"> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #00d8ff\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #ff5e00\">&lt; 고구마요리로~&nbsp;스프도 있답니다~~&gt;</span></